Package org.easybatch.jms

This package contains JMS support classes.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BroadcastJmsRecordDispatcher
    Broadcast records to a list of Jms queues.
    ContentBasedJmsRecordDispatcher
    Dispatch records to a list of Jms Queues based on their content.
    ContentBasedJmsRecordDispatcherBuilder
    Builder for ContentBasedJmsRecordDispatcher.
    JmsMessageTransformer
    Convenient processor that creates a JmsRecord with TextMessage payload from a StringRecord.
    JmsPoisonMessage
    A End-Of-Stream Message implementation .
    JmsPoisonRecord
    End-Od-Stream Jms record.
    JmsPoisonRecordBroadcaster
    A utility job listener that broadcasts a JmsPoisonRecord at the end of the job.
    JmsPoisonRecordFilter
    Filter JmsPoisonRecord.
    JmsQueueConnectionListener
    Listener that closes a JMS queue connection at the end of the job.
    JmsQueueRecordReader
    A record reader that reads records from a JMS queue.
    JmsQueueRecordWriter
    Sends a Jms message to a given queue.
    JmsQueueSessionListener
    Listener that closes a JMS queue session at the end of the job.
    JmsRecord
    Record containing a JMS Message as payload.
    RandomJmsRecordDispatcher
    Dispatch records randomly to a list of Jms queues.
    RoundRobinJmsRecordDispatcher
    Dispatch records to a list of Jms queues in round-robin fashion.
